oherence and measurement problems\nwhich was tackled unsuccessfully by many famous mathematicians and physicists\nstarting with von Neumann, Schroedinger and Bohr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2002 18:51:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2002 20:41:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
